* Mother: {{ill|Kasuga no Ōiratsume no Ōkimi|ja|春日大娘皇女|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=draft}} (Princess of {{ill|Emperor Yūryaku|ja|雄略天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=draft}})
* Siblings (same parents): 
